result.name: Clash Royale Chess Theme
result.description:
Clash Royale themed chess.com style. Based off existing chess.com clash theme and colours of pieces inspired by clash chess trailer.
Credit to chess. com for the base: https://www.chess.com/play/computer/clash
Credit to supercell for the colour inspiration: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cYDm_pod2vM
My YouTube channel is linked as the URL. 
Feel free to subscribe, drop a like or watch a video if you wish to support me in my endeavours.
result.notes:
I might possibly revamp this in the future to include the bridge from clash royale as well as a recolour the pieces to be more faithful to the accompanying image.
I also plan to release a Clash of Clans theme.
